---
import FicheLayout from '../../layouts/FicheLayout.astro';

const title = "L'Incohérence des Philosophes — Al-Ghazâlî";
const description = "Analyse critique de la Falsafa par Abû Hâmid Al-Ghazâlî : les 20 questions et les 3 hérésies.";
const fonts = "https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,300;1,400;1,500&family=Cinzel:wght@400;500;600;700;900&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&family=Noto+Naskh+Arabic:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap";
---

<FicheLayout title={title} description={description} fonts={fonts}>
  <nav class="snav">
    <div class="snav-brand">
      <div class="snav-arabic">تهافت الفلاسفة</div>
      <div class="snav-kicker">Fiche de lecture</div>
      <div class="snav-title">L'Incohérence des Philosophes</div>
      <div class="snav-authors">Abû Hâmid Al-Ghazâlî</div>
      <div class="snav-year">◆ 488 H / 1095 C</div>
    </div>

    <span class="snav-lbl">Navigation</span>
    <a href="#bio" class="snav-a on"><span class="snav-bullet"></span>Biographie</a>
    <a href="#contexte" class="snav-a"><span class="snav-bullet"></span>Contexte & Acteurs</a>
    <a href="#questions" class="snav-a"><span class="snav-bullet"></span>Les 20 Questions</a>
    <a href="#heresies" class="snav-a"><span class="snav-bullet"></span>Les 3 Hérésies</a>
    <a href="#concepts" class="snav-a"><span class="snav-bullet"></span>Concepts Clefs</a>
    <a href="#heritage" class="snav-a"><span class="snav-bullet"></span>Héritage & Réception</a>

    <div class="snav-score">
      <div class="snav-score-title">Analyse du texte</div>
      <div class="score-label"><span>Questions critiques</span><span>20</span></div>
      <div class="score-bar"><div class="score-fill" style="width:100%; background:var(--gold)"></div></div>
      <div class="score-label" style="margin-top:.6rem"><span>Hérésies (Kufr)</span><span>3</span></div>
      <div class="score-bar"><div class="score-fill" style="width:15%; background:var(--ruby)"></div></div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="main">
    <section id="hero" class="hero-ghazali">
      <div class="hero-diag"></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-tag">Philosophie islamique médiévale · Kalâm & Falsafa</div>
        <div class="hero-arabic-title">تهافت الفلاسفة</div>
        <h1 class="hero-h1">
          <span class="line1">L'Incohérence</span>
          <span class="line2">des</span>
          <span class="line3">Philosophes</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="hero-rule"></div>
        <p class="hero-sub">
          L'œuvre où <strong>Al-Ghazâlî</strong> utilise la logique contre elle-même pour démontrer l'incapacité de la raison à trancher les questions métaphysiques.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-chips">
          <span class="chip">Asharisme</span>
          <span class="chip">Réfutation d'Avicenne</span>
          <span class="chip">Occasionnalisme</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="bio" class="sec">
      <div class="sec-eyebrow">
        <span class="sec-num">01</span>
        <h2 class="sec-h2">Abû Hâmid Al-Ghazâlî</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="bio-grid">
        <div class="bio-card">
          <h3>La crise de Baghdâd</h3>
          <p>Au sommet de sa gloire à la Nizâmiya, il est frappé par une aphasie psychosomatique en 1095. Il abandonne tout pour une vie d'errance soufie pendant 10 ans.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bio-card">
          <h3>La méthode interne</h3>
          <p>Ghazâlî ne rejette pas la logique. Il l'étudie en profondeur (<em>Maqâsid al-Falâsifa</em>) avant de la retourner contre les philosophes grecs (<em>Tahâfut</em>).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="heresies" class="sec alt" style="background: var(--ruby2); color: white;">
      <div class="sec-eyebrow">
        <span class="sec-num" style="color: var(--gold)">02</span>
        <h2 class="sec-h2" style="color: white">Les 3 points de rupture (Kufr)</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="heresies-container">
        <div class="heresy-item">
          <span class="heresy-num">01</span>
          <h4>L'Éternité du monde</h4>
          <p>L'affirmation que l'univers n'a pas de commencement temporel, niant la création <em>ex nihilo</em>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="heresy-item">
          <span class="heresy-num">02</span>
          <h4>L'Omniscience limitée</h4>
          <p>La thèse d'Avicenne selon laquelle Dieu ne connaît les particuliers que de manière universelle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="heresy-item">
          <span class="heresy-num">03</span>
          <h4>Négation de la résurrection</h4>
          <p>Le refus d'admettre la résurrection physique des corps, réduite à une métaphore.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="concepts" class="sec">
      <div class="sec-eyebrow">
        <span class="sec-num">03</span>
        <h2 class="sec-h2">Le feu et le coton</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="concept-focus">
        <p class="pq">
          "Le lien entre ce qu'on appelle habituellement la cause et ce qu'on appelle l'effet n'est pas nécessaire."
          <cite>— Question 17, Sur la causalité naturelle</cite>
        </p>
        <div class="concept-explanation">
          <p>C'est ici que Ghazâlî pose les bases de l'<strong>occasionnalisme</strong>. Le coton ne brûle pas <em>parce que</em> le feu le touche, mais parce que Dieu crée la brûlure <em>au moment</em> du contact. Ce principe préfigure les critiques de David Hume sur l'induction.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</FicheLayout>

<style is:global>
  /* ─── VARIABLES AL-GHAZALI ─── */
  :root {
    --parch: #f5eed8;
    --lapis2: #0f2040;
    --gold: #c89a20;
    --ruby: #8b1a1a;
    --ruby2: #6a1010;
    --ink: #0d0a05;
    --sidebar: 280px;
  }

  body {
    background: var(--parch);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  }

/* ─── SURCHARGE CURSEUR AL-GHAZALI (OR) ─── */
  .cur { 
    width: 12px !important; 
    height: 12px !important; 
    border: 2px solid var(--gold) !important; 
    background: transparent !important; 
    border-radius: 50% !important;
    position: fixed !important; 
    top: 0 !important; 
    left: 0 !important; 
    pointer-events: none !important; 
    z-index: 99999 !important; 
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) !important;
    transition: width 0.3s ease, height 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease !important;
  }
  .cur.expand, .cur.big { 
    width: 44px !important; 
    height: 44px !important; 
    background: rgba(200, 154, 32, 0.15) !important; /* Or translucide au survol */
    border-color: var(--gold) !important; 
  }
  #prog { background: var(--gold) !important; } /* Barre de progression en or */

  /* ─── SIDEBAR (MENU LATÉRAL) ─── */
  .snav {
    position: fixed;
    width: var(--sidebar);
    top: 40px !important; /* Laisse la place à la Navbar globale */
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    background: var(--lapis2);
    color: var(--parch);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow-y: auto;
    z-index: 100;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(200, 154, 32, 0.2);
  }
  .snav-brand { padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
  .snav-arabic { font-family: 'Noto Naskh Arabic', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--gold); text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .snav-kicker { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.55rem; color: var(--gold); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .snav-title { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .snav-authors { font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
  .snav-year { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.55rem; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-top: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; }

  .snav-lbl { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.55rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 1.5rem 2rem 0.5rem; }
  .snav-a { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem; padding: 0.5rem 2rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; transition: all 0.2s; border-left: 2px solid transparent; }
  .snav-a:hover { color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
  .snav-a.on { color: #fff; border-left-color: var(--gold); background: rgba(200,154,32,0.1); }
  .snav-bullet { width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 50%; background: currentColor; }

  .snav-score { margin-top: auto; padding: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
  .snav-score-title { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.55rem; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .score-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .score-bar { height: 3px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 2px; }
  .score-fill { height: 100%; transition: width 0.4s ease; }

  /* ─── MAIN & CONTENU ─── */
  .main {
    margin-left: var(--sidebar);
    background: var(--parch);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  }

  .hero-ghazali {
    min-height: 80vh;
    background: var(--lapis2);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-arabic-title { font-family: 'Noto Naskh Arabic', serif; font-size: 3rem; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: left; }
  .hero-tag { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--gold); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2em; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .hero-h1 { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 4rem; line-height: 0.9; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .hero-h1 .line3 { color: var(--gold); }
  .hero-rule { width: 80px; height: 3px; background: var(--gold); margin: 2rem 0; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1.2rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width: 700px; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic; }
  .hero-sub strong { color: #fff; font-style: normal; }
  
  .hero-chips { display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; margin-top: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .chip { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.55rem; padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem; border: 1px solid var(--gold); color: var(--gold); background: rgba(200,154,32,0.1); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }

  .sec { padding: 5rem 4rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .sec-eyebrow { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .sec-num { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; opacity: 0.1; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1;}
  .sec-h2 { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--ink); }

  .bio-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .bio-card { background: white; padding: 2rem; border-top: 3px solid var(--gold); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
  .bio-card h3 { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--lapis2); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .bio-card p { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; }

  .heresies-container { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
  .heresy-item { padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
  .heresy-num { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--gold); display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1;}
  .heresy-item h4 { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .heresy-item p { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; opacity: 0.9;}

  .pq { font-style: italic; font-size: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--gold); padding-left: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; line-height: 1.5;}
  .pq cite { display: block; margin-top: 1rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); font-style: normal; }
  .concept-explanation { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 800px; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    :root { --sidebar: 0px; }
    .snav { display: none; }
    .main { margin-left: 0; }
    .bio-grid, .heresies-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-ghazali { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .sec { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>